    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉政府被指控将抗震救灾政治化</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/28/world/americas/venezuela-quake-relief-rodriguez.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[批评人士称，该国临时总统德尔西·罗德里格斯正试图利用这场悲剧谋取政治利益。她的支持者指责反对派也这样做。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/28/world/americas/venezuela-quake-relief-rodriguez.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jun 2026 09:00:58 GMT</pubDate>
