    <item>
      <title>纽约最热门的竞选地点是哪里？俱乐部。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/28/nyregion/whats-the-hottest-spot-in-new-york-for-campaigning-the-club.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佐兰·马姆达尼去年就做到了。克莱尔·瓦尔迪兹（Claire Valdez）最近竞选国会议员时也是如此。一些候选人在天黑后进行竞选活动以吸引年轻选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/28/nyregion/whats-the-hottest-spot-in-new-york-for-campaigning-the-club.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jun 2026 07:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朱莉娅·莱特洛 (Julia Letlow) 在特朗普的提拔下赢得路易斯安那州共和党参议院决选</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/27/us/louisiana-senate-republican-runoff-results.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果莱特洛女士进入参议院，她将取代参议员比尔·卡西迪，成为第一位共和党议员。妇女在会议厅代表路易斯安那州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/27/us/louisiana-senate-republican-runoff-results.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jun 2026 02:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
